Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.12,0:24:13.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}遺失了開啟樂園的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:18.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}接受懲罰死去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.82,0:24:22.46,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}向著深夜的迷途
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.40,0:24:27.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}無法忍受的荊棘
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.02,0:24:31.45,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}鬆開的鎖鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.62,0:24:41.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}追尋著永遠被埋葬的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.91,0:24:50.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}請不要看這殘破的我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.09,0:24:59.92,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}破裂的牽絆 黑色的安魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.31,0:25:09.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}請不要來這裡 這你未知的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.57,0:25:16.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}下著絕望的雨的世界……
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.55,0:25:17.95,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}現在、完結
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.13,0:25:23.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}如火焰般閃耀於汝等心中
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.03,0:25:25.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}主宰汝等…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.12,0:24:13.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}楽園の扉開く　鍵を　失くして
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:18.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}罰を受けし心は
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.82,0:24:22.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}夜の迷路へ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.40,0:24:27.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}茨の王　赦さず
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.02,0:24:31.45,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}解けめ鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.62,0:24:41.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}求めたのは　永遠　埋めたは愛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.91,0:24:50.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}穢れ壊れた　僕をみないで
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.09,0:24:59.92,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}裂かれた絆　黒きレクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.31,0:25:09.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}ここにこないで　君は知らないで
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.57,0:25:16.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}絶望の雨が降れる　世界が……
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.55,0:25:17.95,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}今、終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.13,0:25:23.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}Which Shinetu as a flame in the midst of your palace
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.03,0:25:25.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}And reigneth Amongst…
